#: {{uxi|fi|Olen '''vapaa''' mies.|I am a '''free''' man.}}
# [[free]] {{gloss|unconstrained}}
#: {{uxi|fi|Hänelle annettiin '''vapaat''' kädet tehdä, mitä hän haluaa.|He was given '''free''' rein to do whatever he wanted.}}
# [[free]] {{gloss|released}}
#: {{uxi|fi|Päästimme kanin '''vapaaksi'''.|We set the rabbit '''free'''.}}
# [[free]], [[off]] {{gloss|without obligations}}
#: {{uxi|fi|Voit pitää loppupäivän '''vapaata'''.|You can take the rest of the day '''off'''.}}
# [[spare]], free {{gloss|not filled with activity or work}}
#: {{uxi|fi|Minulla on paljon '''vapaa'''-aikaa.|I have a lot of '''free''' time.}}
# [[vacant]]
#: {{uxi|fi|Istuin on '''vapaa'''.|The seat is '''vacant'''.}}
# [[unmarried]], [[single]]
# [[free-range]] {{gloss|of, pertaining to, or produced by animals that are allowed to roam freely, rather than being confined indoors}}
#: {{uxi|fi|Ostan aina '''vapaan''' kanan munia.|I always buy '''free-range''' eggs.}}
